Package: Rlda
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian LDA for mixed-membership clustering analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Pedro Albuquerque and Denis Valle
Maintainer: Pedro Albuquerque <pedroa@unb.br> and Denis Valle <drvalle@ufl.edu>
Description: The goal of this packageis to describe the Bayesian LDA model for
    mixed-membership clustering based on different types of data (i.e., Multinomial, Bernoulli,
    and Binomial entries).
License: GPL-2
LazyData: TRUE
Depends:  R (>= 2.10), Rcpp (>= 0.9.4), RcppProgress (>= 0.1)
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp,
    RcppArmadillo,
    RcppProgress
Imports:
    RcppArmadillo,
    gtools
SystemRequirements: GNU make
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
